The Landlord asked us to find out the reasons of these abnormal happenings. To investigate not only monsters but also the entire area, try to contact fairies through other mediums instead of contacting Marrow.

Well... bring crystals from Mudfrog in Larksdowns. You can get them, if you catch the frog first. They are not hard to find if you go out to Larksdowns, so you can get them easily. Getting crystals would be harder than getting Marrow. I will explain the reasons after you come back.

The door to Larksdowns is on the west side of the town. Do you know Jeremia from the trading office? If you pass by Jeremia, just look to the right side and you will see the door.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;I wouldn&amp;amp;#039;t use this way if monsters weren&amp;amp;#039;t become violent. Mudfrogs are at the beach of Larksdowns.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;You have brought the crystals! Good work.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</oldversion><newversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
