The reason why to get crystal is harder? &amp;amp;lsquo;Marrow&amp;amp;rsquo; remains in fairies memories on monsters, but a crystal is a little different from them. It is made by the interconnection between a fairy of a living being and a fairy of the area. Marrow is in everything, but crystals rarely exist. They give you detailed memories of circumstances while merrow only has a memory of a certain living thing. A little difficult? You will get these as time passes.

Please bring the crystal of Fragys. To get them, you need to hunt Fragys as you hunted the Mudfrogs. Fragys are in Logging Site, east of Larksdowns. Please be careful.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;It will be a long journey. Hope for the best.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Did you bring the Fragy&amp;amp;#039;s crystal? This will make us find out about the ground of Larksdowns and the living creatures. I hope there are no other sacrifices.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</oldversion><newversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
