&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;questlistid&gt;Soular007&lt;/questlistid&gt;&lt;Title&gt;Delivering the Report&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Delivering the report to the lord, Lionel&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;Through the crystal, we could find out about the fairies and the land condition of Larksdowns. The faries of Larksdowns and Weed Ridge are afraid of the same thing.

There is something dreadful in the Fox Den in the middle of the island. The reason for which the Red Foxes left their cave was the same. Something in the cave, which is unknown to me and even to the fairies of this island. I sense that it has dramatic power and a fearful evil will. This unknown power chased the souls away from the Fox Den and it&amp;amp;#039;s surroundings and made monsters without spirit to slaves. Unruled monsters captivated by fear are losing reason.

We, the humans have to do something about it.
Deliver this to to the lord, Lionel.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;I hope this report will change Lionel&amp;amp;#039;s mind about these creatures. Do your best.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;A letter from the master of the Divine Association. Okay, I will read it.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</oldversion><newversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
