&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;questlistid&gt;ac1gt004&lt;/questlistid&gt;&lt;Title&gt;Delivery of Jeremiah&amp;amp;#039;s Account Book (1)&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Receive Tricia&amp;amp;#039;s account book&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;As you can see, the trading post is always crowded. It&amp;amp;#039;s always noisy and lively because of the people from other islands, who have come to look for prices and also merchants trying to buy materials that adventurers like yourself have collected. Under these circumstances it is very hard to match the proper price and volume. I&amp;amp;#039;m one of the few who can handle this without any big problems. Unfortunately, since I&amp;amp;#039;m a very busy man it&amp;amp;#039;s impossible for me to pay attention to anything else.

You&amp;amp;#039;ve come right on time, so I&amp;amp;#039;ll ask you a favor. Lori, the Personal Store Manager and Tricia from the Grocery Shop haven&amp;amp;#039;t sent their account books yet and I may have some trouble registering their products on the trading goods list. So I would like you to go and get their account books.

Bring me Tricia&amp;amp;#039;s account book first. Then you&amp;amp;#039;ll have to go to Lori for her&amp;amp;#039;s so please hurry.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Tricia&amp;amp;#039;s Grocery Shop can be found by going straight ahead from the trading post. Please hurry.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Welcome... (nod). We have a lot of things... (nod). Take your time... (nod)&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</oldversion><newversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
