Ah... Jeremiah sent you for it. Why didn&amp;amp;#039;t you say so.
 Excuse me? You did? Yes, I was dozing off but I still can hear everything you say...

Here you go. Give this to him. I&amp;amp;#039;m busy doing business... Yarn...&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;(dozing off)&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Hmm... Let me see. Tricia&amp;amp;#039;s book is completely messed up as I expected. Ordinary people couldn&amp;amp;#039;t recognize what she has written half asleep. Only I can do this... Now, go get Lori&amp;amp;#039;s book.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
