&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;questlistid&gt;ac2gt019&lt;/questlistid&gt;&lt;Title&gt;The Savior in the Past (3)&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Catch Draug Brenin&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;Stone Knight&amp;amp;#039;s Rusty Spear&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;OK. It&amp;amp;#039;s time for the revenge. I will request two things from you.

For one, catch Draug Brenin, the leader of the hateful Draugs. No need to explain more about it, right? If you catch the leader of Draugs, it means our victory over them. It will also end my revenge.

One more thing... Another explorer told me, that he saw a moster called Stone Knight using some kind of spear with a strange picture. The picture looks like a burning key. Being impressed, he brought one of these spears to me, and I realized that it was my missing colleague&amp;amp;#039;s spear.

It means that our soldiers died in the cold basement of the temple and the monsters are using their weapons. I am not sure that having something to remember them makes me feel any better, but I would like you to collect more stuff, belonging to my colleagues, from Stone Knights, especially things belonging to my three best friends.

