&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;questlistid&gt;Soulaa001&lt;/questlistid&gt;&lt;Title&gt;Start of the Adventure (Loading weapons)&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Loading Tutorial Kiriard&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;Loading Tutorial Dagger&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;Changing weapons&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;You are ready to start the adventure?

Uhm.. It seems this is your first time in Florensia.
Well, I will show how to do the basic things first. Please follow my instructions carefully, so that you can expand the saint&amp;amp;#039;s areas of influence.

First of all, to find out how to use weapons, please click the inventory menu box on the right hand side. It is the bag-shaped icon. Alternatively, you can press the l key on the keyboard.

Is the inventory menu box open? Now, drag the mouse to [Tutorial Kiriard] and right-click. You will see the [Tutorial Kiriard] is being loaded on your hand. You can follow the same steps to load [Tutorial Dagger].

If you want to change weapons during the combat, you can press R, or F1, F2, or F3 key on your keyboard.

Now, please go ahead, and try to load weapons and then change weapons.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;Hello. Please drag the mouse to me and right-click.&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Uhm, it seems you are finding it a bit difficult. It&amp;amp;#039;s not as hard as you think, so please keep trying.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Now, you have finished learning how to arm weapons. Let&amp;amp;#039;s move to the next stage.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</oldversion><newversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
