Please click on the face shaped icon above the inventory icon. In the center you can see muscular power, agility, and physical strength etc. with numbers next to it, can&amp;amp;#039;t you? Those numbers are your ability points. Next to the numbers, you will see [+]-shaped buttons. By clicking on each [+] button, you can change your ability points.

Each time you go up a level, you can add 3 points to your ability points. So, make sure to adjust your points when level up. The [ability points] box, showing your points is located under the [LUC] sign. Always keep an eye on your ability points.

Well, then, you can now input your ability points as I just explained to you.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;You have not finished yet? You can take your time. It shouldn&amp;amp;#039;t take too long.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Your ability points are going up now. The sacred power has now been more engergized. The next step is to register skill books.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
