&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;questlistid&gt;Soultu003&lt;/questlistid&gt;&lt;Title&gt;Start of the Adventure (Registering Land Skills)&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Registering Land Skill Books&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;Usage of Land Skill Points&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;With the weapon armed, I can now explain how to use skills.

When you use skills, you can reinforce your offence more strongly and apply various other different abilities during combat. On the right side, there is a sword-shaped icon. Click on that icon to open the skill menu box. The shortcut to open the skill menu box quickly is the K key on the keyboard.

Now, open the inventory menu box. You can find [Magic Text of Healing Hands (For Training)], which I gave to you. Drag the mouse to this skill book and right-click.

As the book disappears from the inventory, the skill shown in the book will be registered in the skill menu box. There is a [+] button next to the registered skill&amp;amp;#039;s icon. When you press this button, the skill will go up to the next skill level. Each skill will cost 1 skill point or more to enable you to use it. Make sure to keep this in mind.

As you advance level by level, you will earn 1 skill point per level. Always check the points when you go up a level. Remember this carefully.

Now then, familiarize youself with using skills.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;I sell skill books required by the saints. You can contact me if you need other skill books later.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Have you finished? Now finally, you can learn how to use the &amp;amp;quot;Quick-slot&amp;amp;quot;s. This will make it easier for you to use skills conveniently.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
