This must be the first time for you to build a ship. So pay attention and follow my instructions carefully!

First, close the chat box, and click on me. This will bring up the [Dock] button. Then click on the [Dock] button. You will arrive at the [Dock], where you can assemble ships.

On the right side of the [Dock] screen, there is the inventory, and on the same side you will find a ship shaped [Small Tutorial Guard Frame]. This is my present to you for having such a high enthusiasm.

Drag the mouse (inside the dock screen) to the Small Guard Frame (top) and right click on it. When a question pops up, asking you &amp;amp;quot;Do you want to register the [Small Tutorial Guard Frame] in the [Dock]?&amp;amp;quot;, obviously you have to press [OK], all right?

This part might be a bit difficult to do. But don&amp;amp;#039;t be scared. Now try to register the battle ship frame, which will form the base of the ship.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Once the frame is registered, you can&amp;amp;#039;t break it down to change it. It will actually be discarded. So choose the one you need carefully.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Have you finished? You are not just enthusiastic, you also have a good eye for this.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</oldversion><newversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
