So, slow down for a moment, and go back to the [Dock] again. When you get there, you will find ship&amp;amp;#039;s main body parts that I have given you. Drag the mouse to [S-shaped Small Tutorial Guard Main Sail], [Grade F Tutorial Demi-Cannon], and [Grade F Tutorial Magic Stone], and right click to open these ship&amp;amp;#039;s body parts. Then, you will find the [Tuning] button flashing at the bottom. Press the [Tuning] button to finish assembling the warship. When the warship assembling is finished, click the Exit button at the bottom.

Now, start assembling the warship.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Learning new things is never easy. Take your time. You&amp;amp;#039;re smart so you will get it very fast, I believe.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Are you finished? Good, good. What is left now is to learn how to load cannon balls. After that, you can set off to the sea.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</oldversion><newversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
